column5: Anyone know where I can rent 16 ft boat and motor in souix lookout area? Is there a marina that will rent or resorts that will rent just boat and motor if not staying at their resort? Thanks!

Northumbrian Resort has older 16' Lund's with 25hp Merc's for rent cheap.http://www.northumbrianresort.com/Moosehorn Resort has really nice boats. There boats are floored and powered by 50hp 4 stroke Yamaha.http://www.canadafish.com/
Do you want a trailer under the boat???
Don't need a trailer if I can rent one on abrams or pelican area.
Try this e-mail: [email protected] They have boats and motor, 25 hp is top size. They are on Pelican at the highway bridge between Pelican and Adrams Lakes.
Thanks, I'll send them an e-mail.
